Class SimpleFeatureUserDataConfigurationSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.adapter.vector.util.SimpleFeatureUserDataConfigurationSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Persistable

    public class SimpleFeatureUserDataConfigurationSet
extends Object
implements Serializable, Persistable
    Represents a set of configurations maintained within the user data of a simple feature type and is tracked by the type name.
